After School Program Assistant
Orleans Elementary School is seeking a part-time afterschool program assistant. This person would assist the Site Director with the following:
· Follow the lead of the Director;
· Prepare and clean up activity spaces as necessary;
· Assist the Director in supervising educational and recreational activities;
· Follow all school and after-school policies and procedures.

This position would be two hours per day from 3:00 – 5:00. Applicants must be 18 years of age, have a high school diploma or equivalent, and complete a background check. Experience working with children is preferred.

Send letter of application with references to Sherrie Gentry, Principal, Orleans Elementary School, 53 School Street, Orleans, VT 05860

